steps.name: Given Coach opened the Gym Management Application
When Coach collect the email and password from config3 properties file
And Coach should click Login button
Then Coach should get a success message "Successfully Logged in"
Then redirected to the workouts list page
When I clicked on the profile icon
Then I Should click on the edit profile button
Then I should fill the form and click on the update button
Then I should see the message profile updated.
